# Shopping App UI (Figma)

## Overview
This is a mobile shopping app UI concept designed in Figma.

## Screens designed
- Splash screen
- Login screen
- Product listing screen
- Scrollable product grid

## What I practiced
- Mobile layout structure
- Scroll behavior
- Image grids
- Basic user flow (login → shop)

## Status
In progress

